values: MASTER WON! Arf! Now Master will gloat around the office for winning two awards, yes? ...Although, Master was acting a little weird when he came home. But it's not that unusual, Arf! Master gets that way sometimes after certain workdays, usually muttering, "Phoenix..." But me, I'm not really sure what that's all about, arf. Master doesn't talk about that stuff. Time to go snooping around the treat bin..Arf! ;)

Master will be receiving his award tonight! I am so excited, ARF!

The house is rather quiet lately. Without the one who calls me Pee Soup and the sister of the one who calls me Pee Soup, it's really not as fun around here. At least now is better than those times Master had to go away. Those were absolutely terrifying. I managed... An award will be given to Master soon for being the King of Prosecutors. I hope to attend the ceremony, but I don't think they allow my kind. It's a shame that they don't let what could be their biggest audience in to see their masters win awards. ~Pess

Does anyone have a letter for me? Arf!

Dear everyone involved in the trial,

Please protect Master. I have been Master's best friend faithfully for a very long time, and I will be hurt if anything happens to Master. I will pay any amount of treats (or whatever Humans put value in, money I suppose) to get Master back at home, and safe. Master has no reason to be in jail. He doesn't poison my water bowl, so he has no reason to poison anyone else's. If anyone knows Master, it is me. He would not harm anyone! Not even a flea!



-From, 
   The more serious side of Pess.

P.S. Mr. Godot! Prosecute anyone else, just don't blame Master!
and Mr. Von Karma -- Just know that I still don't like you, at all! *growl*
